                  <p>On fol. 99 b there is a note, stating that the manuscript belonged to the
                    convent of S. Mary Deipara.</p>
                  <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr"/>
                  </p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition2" n="2">
